parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transfer case can cause the vehicle to lose control, resulting in accidents, or leave the driver stranded. The loss of lubrication can lead to the locking up of wheels, causing the vehicle to slide or become stuck.
symptoms: the vehicle makes a loud noise
the vehicle will not go into drive but will go into reverse
the vehicle slides or becomes stuck

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The exclusion of certain vehicles from the recall (NHTSA Campaign ID Number: 98V069002) may lead to owners being unaware of the potential transfer case failure, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle is not included in the recall despite having the same transfer case issue
the owner is concerned about the safety of their vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature timing belt failure can cause severe engine damage, including bent exhaust valves, damaged heads, and even engine failure, which can lead to costly repairs, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Timing belt breaks or fails prematurely
engine stalls or cuts out while driving
loud noises coming from the engine

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure Due to Valve or Piston Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure due to valve or piston issues can cause the engine to blow, resulting in costly repairs or even requiring a new engine, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: loud noises coming from the engine

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Flywheel/Timing Belt/Engine Turbo and Transmission Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the flywheel, timing belt, engine turbo, and transmission can cause the engine to fail, resulting in costly repairs or even requiring a new engine, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: loud noises coming from the engine

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Camshaft failure can cause engine problems, including stalling and overheating, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: and loud noises coming from the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cooling fan sensor failure can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage or failure, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine overheating and cooling fan problems.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Intermittent stalling can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially if it occurs while driving at high speeds.
symptoms: and loud noises coming from the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the active restraint system can lead to improper deployment or failure of the shoulder belt, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The shoulder belt locks and fails to release
the shoulder belt cannot be used during the first hour of driving
the shoulder belt overtightens against the passenger
the lap/shoulder belt does not retract during a collision.
